These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: d&b, country, ambient, disco, hip-hop, techno
6 different pets are kept: bird, horse, goat, dog, snake, pony
 1. the fan of ambient is in an odd position##4
 2. the fan of techno is somewhere to the left of the fan of country##5
 3. the fan of hip-hop is not the owner of the snake##6
 4. the fan of disco is somewhere to the left of the fan of country##5
 5. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
 6. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
 7. the owner of the snake is not the fan of country##6
 8. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of d&b is somewhere between the owner of the pony and the fan of disco##7
10. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
11. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
12. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
13. the owner of the bird is the fan of d&b##1
14. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5
15. the fan of techno is the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | d&b | ambient   | techno     | country    | hip-hop   |
| Pet           | snake | bird   | pony | dog | goat | horse |

