.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: crime, family, romance, thriller, superhero, spy
6 different pets are kept: frog, hamster, rabbit, rat, turtle, goat
 1. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
 2. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
 3. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
 4. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
 5. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
 7. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
 8. the person watching crime movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching superhero movies is not the owner of the turtle##6
10. the owner of the frog is somewhere between the owner of the goat and the owner of the rat##7
11. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
12. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
13. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
14. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4
15. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
16. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
17. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere between the owner of the hamster and the person watching superhero movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | spy | thriller | superhero     | romance      | crime |
| Pet           | hamster         | rabbit        | turtle   | rat | frog | goat    |

