.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, almond-milk, coffee, iced-tea, fanta
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: soccer, climbing, cricket, sailing, cycling, weightlifting
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5
 4. the person who's sport is climbing is not the person drinking coffee##6
 5. the person drinking 7up is not the person who's sport is soccer##6
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 7. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
10. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking sprite##7
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
13. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5
14. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | iced-tea        | coffee | fanta    | 7up    | almond-milk | sprite |
| Sport      | climbing | cycling  | weightlifting | sailing | soccer | cricket      |

