 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 2. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 3. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
 4. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 5. the person watching romance movies is not the person drinking cola##6
 6. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking cola##7
 7. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking soy-milk##7
 8. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 9. the person watching family movies is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking fanta##7
10. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
11. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
12. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
13. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person drinking fanta##1
14. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3   |       4       |    5    |   6   |
| Beverage      | fanta | sprite | soy-milk | tea | cola | milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts  | musical      | family | zombie     | spy | romance |

