11. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
12. the person driving the taxi is somewhere between the owner of the mouse and the person driving the helicopter##7
13. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Pet         | fish   | turtle | cat      | ferret | guinea-pig  | mouse   |
| Transport   | bike | snowmobile  | helicopter | subway   | taxi | van |

