.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: writing, hiking, skydiving, dancing, card-games, singing
The people have 6 different jobs:  doctor, engineer, electrician, librarian, chef, photographer
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the electrician##5
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere between the librarian and the engineer##7
 5. the photographer is on the left or right of the electrician##3
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the chef##1
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
 8. the chef is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 9. the chef is somewhere to the left of the electrician##5
10. the engineer is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5
11. the photographer is on the right of the electrician##1
12. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
13. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's hobby is skydiving##7
14. the engineer is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
15. the chef is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Hobby   | skydiving         | dancing | hiking | writing   | singing | card-games  |
| Job     | chef | librarian  | electrician  | photographer | engineer  | doctor |

 